definitions.definition: A Titan , the sister-wife of Hyperion .
An Oceanid nymph (daughter of Oceanus and Tethys ), the mother of the Cercopes by Oceanus.
A hypothesised Mars-sized planet of the early solar system thought to have collided with the Earth to produce the Moon .
